{"tid":2396642,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"理大Z座天橋重開　加裝鐵絲網","createTime":"2021-02-05T18:26:30.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-06T03:17:06.000Z","uid":240362,"like":2,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"a47cf7a169bc043cabee7ad10a8058356ed8687b","tid":2396642,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T18:26:30.000Z","msg":"該條行人天橋位於漆咸道南之上，連接賽馬會創新樓和Z座，是由理大主校園直接通往Z座的唯一通道。在理大圍城後，校方曾將天橋長時間封鎖，直至上月31日才重新啟用，但邊緣位置已加設鐵絲圍網，包圍整條天橋，昨仍見有工人進行工程。圍網下方又安裝了多個閉路電視，對準橋下車路。據理大學生報編委會報道，學生需要先拍卡，才能由主校園經天橋通往Z座。<br />\n<br />\n理大校方解釋，大學最近已把連接主校園及Z 座的行人天橋修復，並重新開放予校內師生、員工使用。根據地契要求，大學有責任確保行人天橋的設立，不會影響天橋下漆咸道的交通運作，因此校方在進行修復工程時，也考慮車道安全的需要，在天橋上加裝安全網。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210206/3GIE6PG5QBF4PLABYRIX6ZOQGM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210206%2F3GIE6PG5QBF4PLABYRIX6ZOQGM%2F&d=07E5ZYF2Wb2hLaoCEA3MjNOJZs7QJHlESVJdSYWWwTM%3D&h=bb01da31\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210206%2F3GIE6PG5QBF4PLABYRIX6ZOQGM%2F&h=f80d76ff\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210206/3GIE6PG5QBF4PLABYRIX6ZOQGM/</a>"},{"pid":"9816b4bb9eea90e040ce386f4ae0b5dd84fc5b1a","tid":2396642,"uid":886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T18:34:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"443fab4c34b0105c64eef14da2d6d302adf12bd5","tid":2396642,"uid":84751,"like":10,"dislike":3,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T18:45:04.000Z","msg":"拆左條橋去啦屌, 阻撚住哂, 明明遲下上面可以加多條天橋解決死亡交叉塞車問題, 而家俾條垃圾橋頂住哂"},{"pid":"7d9dd595c0030d34653394656a5e3ea27b8986d0","tid":2396642,"uid":126919,"like":0,"dislike":